<title>hl jrḥ ạlrb yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hl jrḥ ạlrb yswʿ wdmh ạlkrym sạl
 ạ̉mạt sydy ạlwdyʿ wrạ̉sh ạlkrym mạl
 (ạ̉dẖạk ḥbh ạlrfyʿ)2 ly ạ̉nạ yạ lljlạl
 2- whl lạ̉tẖạmy ạ̉nạ qd ṣrkẖ ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 wtḥt ḥmly hl ḥml wdẖạb qlbk ạlḥzyn
 (yạ kẖjly ạ̹dẖạ ạ̉nạ)2 wyạlsydy ạlʿjyb
 3- hl yạ try̱ tfy ạldmwʿ dywn ḥb mn fdy̱
 ḥạsẖạ ạ̉yạ rby yswʿ yạ mnqdẖy mn ạlrdy̱
 (lk ḥyạty fy kẖḍwʿ)2 dẖbyḥẗ ṭwl ạlmdy̱</lyrics>
</song>